% Cost-Accounted Rho — a finite gated-COMM instance (mCRL2). The COMM is GATED by a
% token; a settle follows. Branching-bisimilarity to the rho translation
% (rho_translation.mcrl2) corroborates translation faithfulness up to internal
% steps; the no-leak modal formula (no_leak.mcf) corroborates
% WrappingSubjectReduction.no_leak_requires_token (a COMM cannot fire without a
% co-present token).
act tok, fire, settle;
proc CA = tok . fire . settle . delta;
init CA;
